Diagnose orphan notes (no incoming + no outgoing links)

Usage: obsidian-cli-inspector diagnose orphans [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --exclude-templates  Exclude template notes
      --exclude-daily      Exclude daily notes
  -o, --output <FORMAT>    Output in JSON format (for machine integration)
  -h, --help               Print help
